{
  "texts": [
    "Bayesian inference CoT also demonstrated worse performance than traditional CoT, but the decrease in performance did not meet our significance threshold.",
    "These findings suggest GPT-3.5 is not able to imitate advanced clinical reasoning processes to arrive at an accurate diagnosis.",
    "In contrast, GPT-4 demonstrated similar performance between traditional and diagnostic reasoning CoT prompts.",
    "While these findings highlight the significant advancement in reasoning abilities between GPT-3.5 and GPT-4, diagnostic reasoning does not increase GPT-4 accuracy like it would for a human provider.",
    "We propose three possible explanations for this finding."
  ]
}